author: uschindler
msg: The override of tests.jvms in benchamrk mpodule never worked, so after 2 years of permanent testing with multiple JVMs, the tests are safe.
The override must be placed *before* the inclusion of module-build/common-build.xml, otherwise its to late to redefine the property.
